description: The investment objective of the FT Vest International Equity Moderate Buffer ETF - September (the "Fund") is to seek to provide investors with returns (before fees and expenses) that match the price return of the iShares MSCI EAFE ETF (the "Underlying ETF"), up to a predetermined upside cap of 13.47% while providing a buffer (before fees and expenses) against the first 15% of Underlying ETF losses, over the period from September 23, 2024 through September 19, 2025.
name: FT Vest International Equity Moderate Buffer ETF - September
